<HEADLINE> Mexico 5, Saudi Arabia 1 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	MEXICO CITY (AP) -- Cuauhtemoc Blanco scored four goals and Jose  
Manuel Abundis also scored as Mexico routed Saudi Arabia 5-1 Sunday 
in the FIFA Confederations Cup. 
</P>
<P>
	Egypt and Bolivia played a 2-2 tie in the other game of the  
first-round doubleheader. 
</P>
<P>
	Blanco scored in the 10th, 18th, 67th and 77th minutes, and  
